f--second">By <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><span class="author"><a href="/chef/jane-hornby">Jane Hornby</a></span></span></span></div><div class="recipe-header__magazine"> <a href="//www.buysubscriptions.com/print/bbc-good-food-magazine-subscription?promo=GFBS718&amp;style=Brand&amp;utm_medium=brandsite&amp;utm_source=bbcgoodfood.com&amp;utm_campaign=recipe_GFBS718_Brand&amp;utm_content=recipe-banner" rel="external" onclick="Drupal.GFAnalytics.trackEvent(['Magazines', 'subscribe', 'Recipeheader' ])"> Magazine subscription  5 issues for 5 </a></div></div><div class="recipe-header__details-second"><div class="recipe-details"> <section class="recipe-details__item recipe-details__item--cooking-time"><div class="recipe-details__text"><h2 class="element-invisible"></h2> <span class="recipe-details__cooking-time-prep"> <strong>Prep:</strong> <span class="mins">10 mins</span> </span> <span class="recipe-details__cooking-time-cook"> <strong>Cook:</strong> <span class="mins">15 mins</span> </span></div> </section> <section class="recipe-details__item recipe-details__item--skill-level"><h2 class="element-invisible"></h2> <span class="recipe-details__text"> Easy </span> </section> <section class="recipe-details__item recipe-details__item--servings"><h2 class="element-invisible"></h2> <span class="recipe-details__text" itemprop="recipeYield"> Serves 4 </span> </section><meta itemprop="sourceOrganization" content="BBC Good Food" /><meta itemprop="accountablePerson" content="BBC Good Food" /><meta itemprop="datePublished" content="2005-10-01" /><meta itemprop="cookTime" content="PT15M" /><meta itemprop="prepTime" content="PT10M" /><meta itemprop="totalTime" content="PT25M" /><meta itemprop="cookingMethod" content="Spicy" /><meta itemprop="recipeCuisine" content="Indian" /><meta itemprop="recipeCategory" content="Dinner" /><meta itemprop="recipeCategory" content="Lunch" /><meta itemprop="recipeCategory" content="Snack" 