/lentil"><div class="vertical-push-item__image"> <img src="//www.bbcgoodfood.com/sites/default/files/styles/carousel_medium/public/recipe-collections/collection-image/2013/05/beetroot-lentil-tabbouleh_1.jpg?itok=2PhxEi53" width="468" height="382" alt="Beetroot &amp; lentil tabbouleh on a plate" title="Lentil recipes" /> <span class="vertical-push-item__badge vertical-push-item__badge--type">Collection</span></div><h3 class="vertical-push-item__title"> Lentil</h3><div class="vertical-push-item__count"> 42 Recipes</div> </a></article><article id="node-4045091" class="vertical-push-item vertical-push-item--carousel node node-recipe-collections node-large-push-item clearfix"> <a href="/recipes/collection/carrot"><div class="vertical-push-item__image"> <img src="//www.bbcgoodfood.com/sites/default/files/styles/carousel_medium/public/recipe-collections/collection-image/2014/02/carrot-salad.jpg?itok=j6jhLwVC" width="468" height="382" alt="Roasted carrot, rocket and lentil salad in a dish" title="Carrot recipes" /> <span class="vertical-push-item__badge vertical-push-item__badge--type">Collection</span></div><h3 class="vertical-push-item__title"> Carrot</h3><div class="vertical-push-item__count"> 49 Recipes</div> </a></article><article id="node-103381" class="vertical-push-item vertical-push-item--carousel node node-recipe-collections node-large-push-item clearfix"> <a href="/recipes/collection/soup"><div class="vertical-push-item__image"> <img src="//www.bbcgoodfood.com/sites/default/files/styles/carousel_medium/public/recipe-collections/collection-image/2013/05/mushroom-potato-soup-440-400.jpg?itok=T-yronzu" width="468" height="382" alt="Mushroom &amp; potato soup in a blue bowl" title="Soup recipes" /> <span class="vertical-push-item__badge vertical-push-item__badge--type">Collection</span></div><h3 class="vertical-push-item__title"> Soup</h3><div class="vertical-push-item__count"> 53 Recipes</div> </a></article><article id="node-3976061" class="vertical-push-item vertic