w-display-id-comment_page view-dom-id-8cb8bf56af38052f210b0349449ec088"><div class="view-content"><div><div id="comment-wrapper-1053046"><a id="comment-1053046"></a><article class="comment"> <header class="comment__header"><div class="comment__author-picture"> <span class="comment__author-picture--no-login"></span></div><div class="comment__author-name"> <span class="username">RLakhs</span></div><div class="comment__date"> 28th Apr, 2018</div> </header><div class="comment__text"><div class="field field-name-comment-body field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">Delicious but even more so with the following additions/tips:
Add 1/3 tsp coriander seeds with the cumin seeds and chilli flakes.
Saut: 1 chopped onion 4 garlic cloves (minced)
Add 2 small/medium sweet potato (chopped)
Dont bother grating carrot. Throw it in roughly chopped.
Whizz everything together.
You can also use toor daal (yellow lentil) in place of red lentil. Theyre both good.
Lovely warming soup!</div></div></div></div> </article></div></div><div><div id="comment-wrapper-1048826"><a id="comment-1048826"></a><article class="comment"> <header class="comment__header"><div class="comment__author-picture"> <span class="comment__author-picture--no-login"></span></div><div class="comment__author-name"> <span class="username">disaster chef</span></div><div class="comment__date"> 18th Mar, 2018</div> </header><div class="comment__rating-and-report-wrapper"><div class="comment__rating"><div class="rate-widget rate-widget-fivestar clear-block rate-processed"><div class="fivestar-bbcgoodfood"><div class="clearfix fivestar-widget-static fivestar-widget-static-vote fivestar-widget-static-5"><div class="star star-1 star-odd star-first"><span class="on">5.05</span></div><div class="star star-2 star-even"><span class="on"></span></div><div class="star star-3 star-odd"><span class="on"></span></div><div class="star star-4 star-even"><span class="on"></span></div><div class="star star-5 star-odd star-last"><span class="on"></span></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="comment__text"><div class="field field-name-comment-body field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">Easy and tasty, will add a touch more chilli next time.....</div></div></div></div> </article></div></div><div><div id="comment-wrapper-1047031"><a id="comment-1047031"></a><article class="comment"> <header class="comment__header"><div class="comment__author-picture"><div class="user-picture"> <img src="//www.bbcgoodfood.com/sites/default/files/styles/avatar/public/pictures/picture-6880946-1520594578.jpg?itok=R3A_RSh6" width="40" height="40" alt="john smith&#039;s picture" title="john smith&#039;s picture" /></div></div><div class="comment__author-name"> <span class="username">john smith</span></div><div class="comment__date"> 9th Mar, 2018</div> </header><div class="comment__text"><div class="field field-name-comment-body field-type-