ixon</span></div><div class="comment__date"> 23rd Sep, 2016</div> </header><div class="comment__text"><div class="field field-name-comment-body field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">Delicious! I used coconut milk (the drinking kind) rather than cows milk. The hint of coconut really helped the flavour.</div></div></div></div> </article></div></div><div><div id="comment-wrapper-920891"><a id="comment-920891"></a><article class="comment"> <header class="comment__header"><div class="comment__author-picture"> <span class="comment__author-picture--no-login"></span></div><div class="comment__author-name"> <span class="username">Atay</span></div><div class="comment__date"> 27th Apr, 2016</div> </header><div class="comment__rating-and-report-wrapper"><div class="comment__rating"><div class="rate-widget rate-widget-fivestar clear-block rate-processed"><div class="fivestar-bbcgoodfood"><div class="clearfix fivestar-widget-static fivestar-widget-static-vote fivestar-widget-static-5"><div class="star star-1 star-odd star-first"><span class="on">5.05</span></div><div class="star star-2 star-even"><span class="on"></span></div><div class="star star-3 star-odd"><span class="on"></span></div><div class="star star-4 star-even"><span class="on"></span></div><div class="star star-5 star-odd star-last"><span class="on"></span></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="comment__text"><div class="field field-name-comment-body field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">Fantastic recipe - cheap, easy, tasty and healthy - I made it vegan by swapping the dairy milk for a tin of coconut milk. This has become a regular of mine and has been a big hit with friends.</div></div></div></div> </article></div></div><div><div id="comment-wrapper-874901"><a id="comment-874901"></a><article class="comment"> <header class="comment__header"><div class="comment__author-picture"> <span class="com